{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"051001a28f","title":"给卫道者","origin":"《重庆市右派言论选辑第一集》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共重庆市委宣传部办公室编印，1957年8月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a60b4eed87","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":18,"articleId":"051001a28f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7fe8902b9e","name":"重庆师范专科学校"},{"id":"eece9b3d9e","name":"钟家源"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"27b3ef14e1","type":"title","text":"给卫道者","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"74ca587ad4","type":"authors","text":"重庆师范专科学校钟家源","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"4dd9e045e0","type":"paragraph","text":"[编者按：钟家源，地主出身，重庆师专学生，曾于1950年混入青年团，在土地改革中，害怕被土匪杀害撕毁组织介绍信，脱团并脱离革命，鸣放中反说他“上了青年团的当，受了骗，团污得很”。有人出来对鸣放中的错误言论说了几句公道话，他就写了这首诗加以恶毒的咒骂。]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"1f1905fa38","type":"paragraph","text":"告诉你","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"cb4192b81f","type":"paragraph","text":"你披着马列主义的外衣","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"2f76a95b94","type":"paragraph","text":"给敌人做着忠实的奴隶","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"12ed5414f3","type":"paragraph","text":"你决不帮助党整风","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"f6bc5b1ff2","type":"paragraph","text":"你决心保卫“特权阶级”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"ba00879de9","type":"paragraph","text":"请你到清水池边","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"3b39872886","type":"paragraph","text":"照照你那狰狞的面皮","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"908bb2b85a","type":"paragraph","text":"你自以为很有道理","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"575c22474a","type":"paragraph","text":"其实","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"e3a0a0b2f4","type":"paragraph","text":"都是些十七世纪遗留下的臭东西","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"240c3ad21e","type":"paragraph","text":"你象飘飘在虚空的孔明灯","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"5e2be780b9","type":"paragraph","text":"一肚子灌满了乌烟瘴气","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"7c3f4fa198","type":"paragraph","text":"你把他当成了“皇经皇籍”","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"f05ea9b4ba","type":"paragraph","text":"当成了卫道的武器","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"7361563dd1","type":"paragraph","text":"时代的狂潮象惊天动地的飘下","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"d5dcbc05ff","type":"paragraph","text":"它要掀翻你","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"4212f2221b","type":"paragraph","text":"摔碎你","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"3166560667","type":"paragraph","text":"把你从十万公尺的高空","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"3db74f42b4","type":"paragraph","text":"摔向那活世界的水底","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"c026e24026","type":"paragraph","text":"摔得你粉身碎骨","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"636373e1d9","type":"paragraph","text":"我们将见你做一堆儿肉饼","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"d714c80615","type":"paragraph","text":"堆在那里腐烂、生蛆","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"},{"id":"a7fdb7077c","type":"paragraph","text":" 6．18","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f"}],"page":{"id":"ce414b5fa8","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"051001a28f","start":0,"end